---
title: Smart Jalapeño and Feta Double Chicken Patties with Charred Corn Salad and Southwest Aioli
description: These delightful chicken fritters get a little heat from the jalapeños, a hit of smokiness from the charred corn and a touch of saltiness from the feta. Pan-fry them to golden perfection, then serve them alongside a fresh salad for a super-satisfying meal.

